   139‚Üí## Versions
   141‚ÜíA "version" is described by the `v2.0.0` specification found at
   142‚Üí<https://semver.org/>.
   143‚Üí
   144‚ÜíA leading `"="` or `"v"` character is stripped off and ignored.
   145‚ÜíSupport for stripping a leading "v" is kept for compatibility with `v1.0.0` of the SemVer
      ‚Üí‚Ä¶
   148‚Üí## Ranges
   150‚ÜíA `version range` is a set of `comparators` that specify versions
   151‚Üíthat satisfy the range.
   152‚Üí
   153‚ÜíA `comparator` is composed of an `operator` and a `version`.  The set
   154‚Üíof primitive `operators` is:
      ‚Üí‚Ä¶
