   384‚Üí### Range Grammar ‚Ä¶
   408‚Üí## Functions
   410‚ÜíAll methods and classes take a final `options` object argument.  All
   411‚Üíoptions in this object are `false` by default.  The options supported
   412‚Üíare:
   413‚Üí
   414‚Üí- `loose`: Be more forgiving about not-quite-valid semver strings.
